Package: distancemeasures
Type: Package
Title: Plot various distance measures in regression context (Cooks, DFFITS,Hadis)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Corvin Idler, corvin.idler@gmail.com
Maintainer: corvin.idler@gmail.com
Description: The aim of the package is be to create a graph similar to a Cooks distance plot but with more distance
measures.
The user will provide the program with a data set as well as a model (which is an object of class lm)
The functionality of the program entail performing a simple diagnostics on the influence of points.
The package is be able to calculate at least three measures of influence:
• Cooks Distance Measure (Cook, 1977)
• DFFITS (Welsch and Kuh, 1977; Belsley, 1980)
• Hadis Influence Measure (Hadi, 1992
License: `use_gpl3_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
